Also convert copy_{from,to}_user() of 1 and 2 byte variables to {get,put}_user().
Signed-off-by: Alexey Dobriyan <adobriyan@mail.ru>
Index: linux-2.6.11-rc4-bk9-warnings/drivers/char/sonypi.c
===================================================================
